  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/ed24d54b1e7e6590f45bea7f6fd5b615.avif?t=1684861555\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>During a vegetable contest in the Middle Ages, one of the participants tried to cheat by casting a spell to make their vegetables bigger. It fails and ends up bringing the vegetables to life. Due to this situation, the villagers call Megi, a powerful little traveling witch with magic powers in order to protect their hoses and finish with the vegetable’s invasion. <br><br>To do this, Megi will need to go through the outside of the village into the main castle trying to find the invasion’s origin and defeat the vegetables that are haunting the villagers, bringing everything back to normal.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/a40fc13b180859695c853dd6bb194d1f.avif?t=1684861555\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Cartoony medieval and fantasy-themed 2D run-and-gun platformer<br></li><li> Play cooperatively with the supported 2-player Local coop mode<br></li><li> Featured abilities: fast speed, quick-dash ability, and powerful magic projectiles!<br></li><li> Languages: English, Spanish, Finish, Polish, Catalan, Basque</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/5e0563314beb064e16a12a98d98c3c2f.poster.avif?t=1684861555\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/5e0563314beb064e16a12a98d98c3c2f.webm?t=1684861555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/5e0563314beb064e16a12a98d98c3c2f.mp4?t=1684861555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/be67dd0a022ee0215b8e52c0afc257c3.poster.avif?t=1684861555\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/be67dd0a022ee0215b8e52c0afc257c3.webm?t=1684861555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/be67dd0a022ee0215b8e52c0afc257c3.mp4?t=1684861555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/eda035fab55dc2e5bea4da4051c84b41.poster.avif?t=1684861555\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/eda035fab55dc2e5bea4da4051c84b41.webm?t=1684861555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/eda035fab55dc2e5bea4da4051c84b41.mp4?t=1684861555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/a0314dc9cb71f37107ea1d9189626940.avif?t=1684861555\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/36dba6a99dbb13d01cd01afb3296b0d0.avif?t=1684861555\" width=599 height=175 /></span><br><br>Veggie Menace is a project developed by Pigment Krew, a team of 2nd Year students at DigiPen Institute of Technology Europe - Bilbao in a 9-month development cycle from the ground up using C++ to develop their engine and game.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/ed24d54b1e7e6590f45bea7f6fd5b615.avif?t=1684861555\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>During a vegetable contest in the Middle Ages, one of the participants tried to cheat by casting a spell to make their vegetables bigger. It fails and ends up bringing the vegetables to life. Due to this situation, the villagers call Megi, a powerful little traveling witch with magic powers in order to protect their hoses and finish with the vegetable’s invasion. <br><br>To do this, Megi will need to go through the outside of the village into the main castle trying to find the invasion’s origin and defeat the vegetables that are haunting the villagers, bringing everything back to normal.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/a40fc13b180859695c853dd6bb194d1f.avif?t=1684861555\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Cartoony medieval and fantasy-themed 2D run-and-gun platformer<br></li><li> Play cooperatively with the supported 2-player Local coop mode<br></li><li> Featured abilities: fast speed, quick-dash ability, and powerful magic projectiles!<br></li><li> Languages: English, Spanish, Finish, Polish, Catalan, Basque</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/5e0563314beb064e16a12a98d98c3c2f.poster.avif?t=1684861555\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/5e0563314beb064e16a12a98d98c3c2f.webm?t=1684861555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/5e0563314beb064e16a12a98d98c3c2f.mp4?t=1684861555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/be67dd0a022ee0215b8e52c0afc257c3.poster.avif?t=1684861555\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/be67dd0a022ee0215b8e52c0afc257c3.webm?t=1684861555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/be67dd0a022ee0215b8e52c0afc257c3.mp4?t=1684861555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/eda035fab55dc2e5bea4da4051c84b41.poster.avif?t=1684861555\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/eda035fab55dc2e5bea4da4051c84b41.webm?t=1684861555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/eda035fab55dc2e5bea4da4051c84b41.mp4?t=1684861555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/a0314dc9cb71f37107ea1d9189626940.avif?t=1684861555\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018490/extras/36dba6a99dbb13d01cd01afb3296b0d0.avif?t=1684861555\" width=599 height=175 /></span><br><br>Veggie Menace is a project developed by Pigment Krew, a team of 2nd Year students at DigiPen Institute of Technology Europe - Bilbao in a 9-month development cycle from the ground up using C++ to develop their engine and game.",
